{"tid":2295162,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"移民劈穿太古，低於銀行估值逾一成才易手","createTime":"2020-11-21T14:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T17:38:08.000Z","uid":73269,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"afcabea37b5b70ea1e290db2c65a978fc2cec962","tid":2295162,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:10:23.000Z","msg":"社會局勢及氣氛不明朗，中產一族掀賣樓移民潮。市場罕見單日連錄3宗業主移民賣樓成交，全屬樓價逾千萬元的中價屋苑。其中荃灣半山屋苑朗逸峯一個近千呎「移民盤」，劈足百萬，低於銀行估值逾一成才易手。鰂魚涌太古城本月移民盤成交比例佔約一成。<br />\n<br />\n美聯吳肇基表示，鰂魚涌太古城本月暫錄15宗成交，估計移民成交佔約兩至三宗，比例逾一成。最新一宗為天星閣中層E室一個面積580方呎兩房則王單位，業主早已移民，今年6月委託在港親友代其放售物業，最初叫價1,250萬元，放盤5個月降價115萬元後，終以1,135萬元售出。"},{"pid":"1066469ee2539e905f35835fa5f8597b52b01b2f","tid":2295162,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ObqlmGQp6rwUlFsJXGYh7XunZEg=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ASOOT3QLFNFCFGVGVCKDWXZJZU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FObqlmGQp6rwUlFsJXGYh7XunZEg%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FASOOT3QLFNFCFGVGVCKDWXZJZU.jpg&h=515e6446&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"befb2fbc81712dcf85fa5d185ea9abdd56d4a906","tid":2295162,"uid":7076,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"前嗰幾日先送咗個朋友上機去英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢賣咗其中一層樓先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb955c56c9e6aae1a8cbded1c018acb94ba12cef","tid":2295162,"uid":359522,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:55:50.000Z","msg":"<del>荃灣</del>半山屋苑都要平賣，樓爆喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bb25d0ddf85ee4c8a7c498757011a70a92c750","tid":2295162,"uid":4826,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:58:44.000Z","msg":"升上劈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3b8307f2934e41afe55bce2f6c45e2a0a5d3fe","tid":2295162,"uid":289946,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:06:32.000Z","msg":"omg...移民潮來了。。。"},{"pid":"8ecd106f461e113db80049bdb6c141a0579b881d","tid":2295162,"uid":357591,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:21:05.000Z","msg":"最新一宗為天星閣中層E室一個面積580方呎兩房則王單位，業主早已移民，今年6月委託在港親友代其放售物業，最初叫價1,250萬元，放盤5個月降價115萬元後，終以1,135萬元售出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大劈完，仲要低銀行估值1成，仲要只係中層<br />\n成交價都差唔多2萬蚊一呎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64aa2f508edfaf6582cd5e240a52f2960353e039","tid":2295162,"uid":134683,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:27:22.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲放負新聞<br />\n上估價網check下啦<br />\n四正啲嘅樓個價硬撚過鐵<br />\n我4個月前賣出個單位少少地都升左十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b603a059d62db94ac0f4f85e5bf1c1714d6107","tid":2295162,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:37:51.000Z","msg":"人哋持貨幾十年賺價賺租<br />\n反而比連登班樓市專家笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970a48d83473c0eb759e8a388a862ccd6da1ff7e","tid":2295162,"uid":374415,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:43:10.000Z","msg":"嘩, 康怡半年前個價都貴過佢, 今次業主福街了"},{"pid":"909ab08b7039aac8c32d237e2a6a086cbcc32453","tid":2295162,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"970a48d83473c0eb759e8a388a862ccd6da1ff7e","t